title: Sumo Salad - QV
typeOfFood: Lacto, Western, Fast food, Salad bar, Take-out, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. Quick service salad restaurant chain. Vegans have choice of 5 salads, raisin toast, soups (in winter), fruit salad, plus cold pressed juices. Labels which dishes are vegan and caters for a range of dietary requirements, all listed on the menu. Salads are pre-made.
